OL,7,FCouncils will be obliged to consider
OL,8,Fwhether residents support the
OL,9,Fimplementation of a Low Traffic
OL,10,FNeighbourhood (LTN) in their area
OL,11,Fbefore schemes can be introduced, the
OL,12,FDepartment for Transport (DfT) has
OL,13,Fannounced.
