OL,7,FLTNs are an area where vehicle numbers
OL,8,Fare reduced, and work by preventing
OL,9,Fvehicles from using certain streets as
OL,10,Fthrough roads into other destinations,
OL,11,Fquite often through using temporary or
OL,12,Fpermanent barriers which stop traffic
OL,13,Ffrom being able to drive along a
OL,14,Fcertain route.
