OL,7,FDfT has published draft statutory
OL,8,Fguidance for councils on LTNs ` to
OL,9,Fcome into force this summer ` setting
OL,10,Fout that they must gain buy-in from
OL,11,Flocal residents, businesses and
OL,12,Femergency services when considering
OL,13,Fimplementing new schemes.
OL,15,FIt comes after a review uncovered a
OL,16,Fraft of concerns over LTNs, including
OL,17,Fpotential risk to life from emergency
OL,18,Fservices delays, impact on disabled
OL,19,Fresidents and high numbers of Penalty
OL,20,FCharge Notices coming out of the
OL,21,Fschemes.
