OL,7,FIn Oxford, and here have been a number
OL,8,Fof protests opposing their
OL,9,Fintroduction.
OL,11,FIf councils fail to deliver road
OL,12,Fschemes that work for local people,
OL,13,Fthey could see future funding
OL,14,Fwithdrawn and the Government could
OL,15,Ftake control of an authority's roads,
OL,16,Funder powers from the Traffic
OL,17,FManagement Act, if they are deemed to
OL,18,Fbe "widely mismanaged", DfT said.
