OL,7,FThe report also found that local
OL,8,Fauthorities operating LTNs issue an
OL,9,Faverage of 36,459 Penalty Charge
OL,10,FNotices per scheme, with the highest
OL,11,Fnumber of notices issued for a single
OL,12,FLTN scheme exceeding 170,000.
OL,14,FThe review further highlighted
OL,15,Fconcerns over the impact on disabled
OL,16,Fresidents and from emergency services
OL,17,Fthat delays to crews caught up in LTNs
OL,18,Fcould "potentially risk lives".
