OL,7,FRishi Sunak called LTNs examples of
OL,8,F"hare-brained schemes" in an interview
OL,9,Fwith The Sun in September last year.
OL,11,FA group of local residents blocked
OL,12,Fcars on a road in Streatham Wells,
OL,13,Fsouth London, in November 2023 as part
OL,14,Fof a protest against the area becoming
OL,15,Fan LTN.
OL,17,FThe scheme was removed, as was an and
OL,18,FDfT said the new guidance aims to
OL,19,Fprevent councils having to reverse
OL,20,Fpoorly-implemented or unpopular
OL,21,Fschemes.
