OL,7,FCouncils have also received
OL,8,F"strengthened guidance" on setting
OL,9,F20mph speed limits, reminding them to
OL,10,Freserve them for sensible and
OL,11,Fappropriate areas only- like outside
OL,12,Fschools ` DfT added.
OL,14,FThe measures come as part of the
OL,15,FGovernment's Plan for Drivers.
OL,17,FTransport Secretary Mark Harper said
OL,18,Fthe Government is on the side of
OL,19,Fdrivers.
