OL,7,F"We want local people to have their
OL,8,Fvoices heard, and any traffic schemes
OL,9,Fto have the consent of those they
OL,10,Fimpact," he said.
OL,12,F"Well thought out schemes, like 20mph
OL,13,Flimits outside schools, can make our
OL,14,Froads safer, but we are raising the
OL,15,Fbar to help ensure all traffic schemes
OL,16,Fwork for everyone in the community.
