OL,7,F"We're on the side of drivers, and
OL,8,Fthese latest measures show we're
OL,9,Fgetting on with delivering what we
OL,10,Fpromised in our Plan for Drivers `
OL,11,Fmaking their lives better, fairer and
OL,12,Fcheaper, and helping people travel in
OL,13,Fthe way that works best for them."
OL,15,FJack Cousens, head of roads policy at
OL,16,FThe AA, said: "The best traffic
OL,17,Fmanagement schemes are the ones which
OL,18,Fhave undergone significant local
OL,19,Fconsultation from their inception."
