OL,7,FHe added: "Allowing more councils to
OL,8,Fimpose fines for yellow box junction
OL,9,Foffences has resulted in some drivers
OL,10,Ffeeling that they are seen as 'wallets
OL,11,Fon wheels' by their local authority."
OL,13,FMr Cousens said the majority of
OL,14,Fdrivers "make honest mistakes" and
OL,15,Fproviding warning letters to first-
OL,16,Ftime offenders "would help educate the
OL,17,Fpublic whilst maintaining trust in
OL,18,Ftown halls".
